author: acmurthy
msg: HADOOP-1874.  Move task-outputs' promotion/discard to a separate thread distinct from the main heartbeat-processing thread. The main upside being that we do not lock-up the JobTracker during HDFS operations, which otherwise may lead to lost tasktrackers if the NameNode is unresponsive. Contributed by Devaraj Das.
